China is the most populated country in the world, so it's no surprise that multiple companies would try to make a profit on the current fad. Business is hardly ever driven by originality, most people just want a slice of a market that already exists. If you can offer any advantage over the competition, such as price, quality or availability, you might be successful at maintaining a business.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Mon May 08, 2017 9:29 am</p><hr />
